==English==
===Etymology===
[[ignorant|ig]] + [[gnostic]] + -[[ism]]

===Noun===
ignosticism

# a form of [[agnosticism]] in which [[theism]] is seen as incoherent because of the [[scientific]] untestability of a god or gods
# ignorance of any knowledge of a god or gods due to finding theism incoherent

